Comments:	Dzen2 was designed to be scriptable in any language and 
		integrate well with window managers like dwm, wmii, and 
		xmondad, though it will work with any window manager.

		Basic Documentation: 
		http://dzen.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/README
		Wiki for advanced topics and example scripts:
		http://dzen.geekmode.org/dwiki/doku.php

		This extension includes the "gadget" programs that come 
		with the dzen2 source code:
		dbar - generates semi-graphical progress meters
		textwidth - calculate the width in pixels of text with 
			    a given font
		gdbar - generates fully graphical progress meters
		gcpubar - CPU utilization meter

